@startuml
title Code Review and Debate
hide footbox
autonumber

skinparam BackgroundColor transparent
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam MaxMessageSize 110
skinparam WrapWidth 220
skinparam RoundCorner 8

actor "Host browser" as Host
actor "Participant browser" as Participant
participant "Railway HTTP proxy" as RailwayHTTP
participant "Daemon code review router" as CodeReviewAPI
participant "Daemon debate router" as DebateAPI
participant "Host local WS" as HostWS
participant "Railway session WS" as RailwayWS
participant "Claude API" as Claude

group Code review
Host -> CodeReviewAPI: POST /host/codereview {snippet, smart_paste}
opt Smart paste enabled
  CodeReviewAPI -> Claude: extract code + detect language
  Claude --> CodeReviewAPI: cleaned snippet, language
end
CodeReviewAPI -> CodeReviewAPI: create review\nset current_activity="codereview"
CodeReviewAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast codereview_opened
CodeReviewAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast activity_updated=codereview

Participant -> RailwayHTTP: PUT /api/participant/codereview/selection
RailwayHTTP -> CodeReviewAPI: proxy line selections
CodeReviewAPI -> CodeReviewAPI: require activity=codereview\nrequire phase=selecting
CodeReviewAPI -> HostWS: host_event codereview_selections_updated

Host -> CodeReviewAPI: PUT /host/codereview/status {open:false}
CodeReviewAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast codereview_selection_closed

Host -> CodeReviewAPI: PUT /host/codereview/confirm-line
CodeReviewAPI -> CodeReviewAPI: confirm line\naward 200 points to matching participants
CodeReviewAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast codereview_line_confirmed
CodeReviewAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast scores_updated
end

group Debate
Host -> DebateAPI: POST /host/debate {statement}
DebateAPI -> DebateAPI: launch debate\nset current_activity="debate"
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_updated
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast activity_updated=debate

Participant -> RailwayHTTP: POST /api/participant/debate/pick-side
RailwayHTTP -> DebateAPI: proxy side pick
DebateAPI -> DebateAPI: auto-assign remaining participants when needed
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: write_back debate_updated

Participant -> RailwayHTTP: POST /api/participant/debate/argument or /upvote or /volunteer
RailwayHTTP -> DebateAPI: proxy debate action
DebateAPI -> DebateAPI: mutate debate state\naward submit/upvote/champion points
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: write_back debate_updated
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: write_back scores_updated

Host -> DebateAPI: POST /host/debate/end-arguments
alt No participant arguments yet
  DebateAPI -> DebateAPI: advance directly to prep
  DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_updated
else Run AI cleanup in background
  DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_updated phase=ai_cleanup
  DebateAPI -> Claude: run_debate_ai_cleanup(statement, for_args, against_args)
  Claude --> DebateAPI: merges + cleaned text + new arguments
  DebateAPI -> DebateAPI: apply AI result and advance to prep
  DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_updated
end

Host -> DebateAPI: POST /phase /first-side /round-timer /end-round
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_updated
DebateAPI -> RailwayWS: broadcast debate_timer / debate_round_ended
end
@enduml
